This paper deals with natural language processing and semantic analysis, which are topics that fall under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of statistical models and machine learning techniques, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. The paper's focus on annotation and corpus creation could also place it in the information retrieval (cs.IR) or cybernetics (cs.CY) categories.
